      <title>苏丹被世界战争肆虐世界已被忽视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/sudan-civil-war-how-the-conflict-began-and-what-its-impact-has-been</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国估计，从那以后，苏丹军队与准军事团体之间的一场长期纠纷爆炸为成熟的内战。从那以后，至少有15万人可能被杀害，而暴力事件几乎没有减轻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/sudan-civil-war-how-the-conflict-began-and-what-its-impact-has-been</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小型企业管理局削减了43％的Doge Push工人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/small-business-administration-to-cut-43-of-workers-in-doge-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小型企业管理局正准备减少其劳动力的43％，理由是埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的政府效率是员工终止的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/small-business-administration-to-cut-43-of-workers-in-doge-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其的埃尔多安（Erdogan）警告反对大规模抗议的呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/turkey-s-erdogan-warns-opposition-over-calls-for-mass-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）警告说，主要反对党在呼吁对伊斯坦布尔市长埃克雷姆·伊玛莫格鲁（Ekrem Imamoglu）拘留的全国性抗议活动后，他不会服从“街头恐怖”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/turkey-s-erdogan-warns-opposition-over-calls-for-mass-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:23:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音说要赢得下一代美国战斗机合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/boeing-said-to-beat-lockheed-for-next-gen-fighter-jet-contract</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，波音公司赢得了一份合同，以设计和建造美国的下一代战斗机，击败了竞争对手洛克希德·马丁公司（Lockheed Martin Corp.）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/boeing-said-to-beat-lockheed-for-next-gen-fighter-jet-contract</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:15:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普官员不需要美国顾问公司的“ Gobbledygook”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/trump-official-targets-booz-allen-accenture-gobbledygook-for-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府正在将其调查升级为联邦咨询公司，包括Booz Allen Handilton Holding Corp.和Accenture Plc，警告公司必须用简单的语言解释他们所做的事情，而不是“术语或Gobbledygook”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/trump-official-targets-booz-allen-accenture-gobbledygook-for-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 14:49:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党人将资金倒入佛罗里达州的比赛中，以侵蚀共和党多数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/democrats-pour-money-into-florida-races-to-erode-gop-majority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据联邦大选委员会的文件，民主党国会候选人在佛罗里达州的一次特别选举中筹集了数百万美元的筹集资金，比共和党的候选人多，强调了种族如何激发渴望在共和党狭窄的众议院多数的党派中挑战一个政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/democrats-pour-money-into-florida-races-to-erode-gop-majority</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 14:27:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋在特朗普会议后承诺1.4万亿美元的美国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/uae-to-pledge-1-4-trillion-us-investment-after-trump-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据白宫称，阿拉伯联合酋长国将在本周早些时候在唐纳德·特朗普总统和阿联酋国家安全顾问谢赫·塔恩·本·扎伊德·纳希扬举行会议之后，将在美国投资1.4万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/uae-to-pledge-1-4-trillion-us-investment-after-trump-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 14:14:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其骚动提示里拉自2023年以来的最糟糕的每周务虚会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/lira-set-for-worst-weekly-drop-since-2023-amid-turkey-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其里拉（Lira）在近两年内每周最陡峭的下降，随着紧急利率的增加未能阻止这种货币在越来越多的政治紧张局势中停止撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/lira-set-for-worst-weekly-drop-since-2023-amid-turkey-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 06:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管停火，但卢旺达支持的叛军扩大了刚果的土地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/rwanda-backed-rebels-expand-control-of-congo-despite-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢旺达支持的M23叛军在刚果民主共和国占领了第三个主要城镇，将其束缚扩大到该国矿产丰富的东部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/rwanda-backed-rebels-expand-control-of-congo-despite-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 05:12:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部说，特朗普内阁在委内瑞拉案中权衡了保密索赔。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/judge-calls-us-filing-woefully-insufficient-in-venezuela-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级司法部官员说，在法官对洛杉矶法院的披露爆炸后，他参与了“内阁级别的讨论”，以援引保密的主张，以掩盖有关驱逐涉嫌委内瑞拉帮派成员的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/judge-calls-us-filing-woefully-insufficient-in-venezuela-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 20:23:06 GMT</pubDate>
